After image rectification has been carried out, the epipolar lines of two projected points are parallel and horizontally aligned along the new image planes.\newline The stereo matching problem is therefore reduced to a one dimensional search along horizontal lines instead of a two dimensional search.\newline Camera images before rectification,pixel matching is a 2D search problem whereas Camera images after rectification,pixel matching can be done through a one dimensional line search.
